svg.text: can indicate a recurrence of an action
or a state over the course of time, e.g.:
天看了一个电影，今天又看了
(Wǒ zuótiān kàn le yí ge diànyǐng, jīntiān
and I watched another one today).
also suggest the augmentation or exacerbation
of certain conditions or circumstances, as in
得那么多，又不运动，当然越
yòu bú yùndòng, dāngrán yuè lái yuè pàng le)
usually eat so much, and on top of that you don’t
exercise; no wonder you’re putting on more and
(Gāo Wénzhōng gēn Wáng Péng liáo tiānr . . . )
Nǐ kàn, wǒ de dùzi yuè lái yuè dà le.
Nǐ píngcháng chī de nàme duō,
dāngrán yuè lái yuè pàng le.
Rúguǒ pà pàng, nǐ yí ge xīngqī yùndòng liǎng, sān
cì, měi cì bàn ge xiǎoshí, dùzi jiù huì xiǎo le.
Zuì jiǎndān de yùndòng shì pǎo bù.
Dōngtiān nàme lěng, xiàtiān nàme rè, pǎo bù tài
Dǎ wǎngqiú děi mǎi wǎngqiú pāi, wǎngqiú xié, nǐ
zhīdao wǎngqiú pāi, wǎngqiú xié guì jí le!
Zhǎo jǐ ge rén dǎ lánqiú ba. Mǎi ge lánqiú hěn
Nà měi cì dōu děi dǎ diànhuà yuē rén, máfan sǐ le.
Nǐ qù yóu yǒng ba. Búyòng zhǎo rén, yě búyòng
huā hěn duō qián, shénme shíhou qù dōu kěyǐ.
Yóu yǒng? Wǒ pà shuǐ, tài wēixiǎn le, yān sǐ le
